---
// Slide 4: New Model - Project-Based Internship
---

<div class="slide-frame inactive w-full" id="slide-4" data-slide="3">
  <div class="space-y-6 max-w-5xl">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end flex-wrap gap-4">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-neonLime uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
          04 // The Paradigm Shift
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-outfit text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
          New Model: Project-Based Internship
        </h2>
      </div>
      <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-users-viewfinder text-neonLime mr-2"></i>Mini Creative Agency
      </span>
    </div>

    <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
      Model baru ini mengubah total cara kerja PKL konvensional dengan
      mengadopsi struktur
      <span class="text-white font-semibold border-b border-neonLime">berbasis proyek nyata dari industri</span>. Siswa dikoordinir dan bekerja layaknya professional dalam
      lingkup agensi kreatif skala mikro.
    </p>

    <!-- Flow Diagram -->
    <div class="pt-6">
      <!-- Mobile/Tablet: 2 columns, Desktop: horizontal flow -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:justify-between gap-3 lg:gap-0">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5 relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neonLime">
            01
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Industry Brief</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute -right-2 top-4 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:top-auto lg:-mr-3 text-slate-700 text-xs"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5 relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
            02
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Creative Expl.</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute -right-2 top-4 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:top-auto lg:-mr-3 text-slate-700 text-xs"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5 relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
            03
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Production</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute -right-2 top-4 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:top-auto lg:-mr-3 text-slate-700 text-xs"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5 relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
            04
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Internal Rev.</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute -right-2 top-4 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:top-auto lg:-mr-3 text-slate-700 text-xs"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5 relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neonIndigo">
            05
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Pitching</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute -right-2 top-4 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:top-auto lg:-mr-3 text-slate-700 text-xs"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 6 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5 relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
            06
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Feedback</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right absolute -right-2 top-4 lg:relative lg:right-auto lg:top-auto lg:-mr-3 text-slate-700 text-xs"></i>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 7 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-2.5">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-neonLime/30 bg-neonLime/10 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-sm font-bold text-neonLime glow-lime">
            07
          </div>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-white tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight">Final Delivery</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
